milestones.description: Afghanistan's 138-run win against Ireland is the largest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 106-run win against Zimbabwe
Dawlat Zadran has broken the record for most ducks (5) in ODIs for AFG, going past Asghar Afghan's 5

stories.title: Mujeeb ready for this stage - Ahmadzai
stories.subTitle: Afghanistan v Ireland, 1st ODI, Sharjah
stories.seoTitle: Mujeeb Zadran ready for this stage - Afghanistan coach Raees Ahmadzai
stories.summary: Afghanistan's teenage offspinner Mujeeb Zadran picked up 4 for 24 on his international debut, and the side's coach Raees Ahmadzai explained that he was given a debut after recent successes with the U-19 side and his work in the nets

stories.title: Teenager Mujeeb Zadran spins out Ireland
stories.subTitle: Afghanistan v Ireland, 1st ODI, Sharjah, December 5, 2017
stories.seoTitle: Teenager Mujeeb Zadran spins out Ireland
stories.summary: The 16-year old debutant turned heads in Sharjah, routing Ireland for 100 in 31.4 overs with figures of 4 for 24
stories.byline: The Report by Peter Della Penna in Sharjah
